change the following lines in p2cool.js to skip ip input screen permanently
//var li = get_cookie('LocalIP');
var li = "yourp2pool:9332";

Preferences such as refresh time, your p2pool address,show/hide 3d graph are stored in the browser cookies. 

Right-arrow on the first page attempts to connect to the specified address. Refresh time and 3d graph spinners work with middle mouse too.

